    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>As a doctrinal concept, the origination of created beings from a deity or spirit in a way that imbues the new being with some of the essence of the deity or spirit; as distinct from act of creation out of nothing. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
